---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="CycleWise — The Partner's Guide to Her Cycle">
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-badge">
        <span class="badge badge-pink">For Partners</span>
      </div>
      <h1>Understand her cycle.<br /><span class="gradient-text">Show up better.</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        CycleWise tracks where she is in her menstrual cycle and tells you exactly what to expect — and what to do about it. Built for partners who want to actually get it right.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="/app" class="btn btn-primary">Start Tracking — Free</a>
        <a href="#how-it-works" class="btn btn-outline">See how it works</a>
      </div>
      <p class="hero-note">🔒 All data stays on your device. We never see it.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Phase orbit visual -->
    <div class="phase-orbit" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="orbit-ring">
        <div class="orbit-phase menstrual">🌑<span>Menstrual</span></div>
        <div class="orbit-phase follicular">🌱<span>Follicular</span></div>
        <div class="orbit-phase ovulation">✨<span>Ovulation</span></div>
        <div class="orbit-phase luteal">🌘<span>Luteal</span></div>
        <div class="orbit-center">🌙</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section class="how-it-works" id="how-it-works">
    <div class="page-wrap">
      <div class="section-label">How it works</div>
      <h2>Three steps to knowing exactly where she is</h2>
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">1</div>
          <h3>Enter her last period date</h3>
          <p>Just the start date. Takes 10 seconds. No account needed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-arrow">→</div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">2</div>
          <h3>See her phase on the calendar</h3>
          <p>The calendar color-codes every day of the month — no guessing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-arrow">→</div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">3</div>
          <h3>Read today's briefing</h3>
          <p>What she may be feeling. What to do. What to avoid. Every single day.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PHASES -->
  <section class="phases-section">
    <div class="page-wrap">
      <div class="section-label">The four phases</div>
      <h2>Every phase decoded for you</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Her cycle has four distinct phases — each with different energy, emotions, and needs. CycleWise explains all of it in plain language.</p>
      <div class="phases-grid">
        <div class="phase-card menstrual-card">
          <div class="phase-emoji">🌑</div>
          <div class="phase-label">Menstrual · Days 1–5</div>
          <h3>Rest &amp; Restore</h3>
          <p>Hormones at their lowest. She needs comfort, patience, and low-key energy. This isn't the time for big plans or hard conversations.</p>
          <div class="phase-tip">💡 Comfort food + heating pad = hero status</div>
        </div>
        <div class="phase-card follicular-card">
          <div class="phase-emoji">🌱</div>
          <div class="phase-label">Follicular · Days 6–13</div>
          <h3>Rising Energy</h3>
          <p>Estrogen is climbing. She's getting more energetic, social, and open to new ideas. Best time to plan dates and have important talks.</p>
          <div class="phase-tip">💡 Book that trip. She's in yes mode.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="phase-card ovulation-card">
          <div class="phase-emoji">✨</div>
          <div class="phase-label">Ovulation · Days 14–16</div>
          <h3>Peak Power</h3>
          <p>She's at her most confident, attractive, and social. A 3-day window where she's radiating. Show up — she'll notice.</p>
          <div class="phase-tip">💡 3 days. Put the phone down.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="phase-card luteal-card">
          <div class="phase-emoji">🌘</div>
          <div class="phase-label">Luteal · Days 17–28</div>
          <h3>Tread Carefully</h3>
          <p>Progesterone rises then crashes. PMS territory in the back half. Emotions run higher. Patience and comfort matter most.</p>
          <div class="phase-tip">💡 Don't say "calm down." Ever.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FREE VS PRO -->
  <section class="pricing-section">
    <div class="page-wrap">
      <div class="section-label">Pricing</div>
      <h2>Start free. Upgrade when it clicks.</h2>
      <div class="pricing-grid">
        <div class="pricing-card free-card">
          <div class="plan-badge">Free Forever</div>
          <div class="plan-price">$0</div>
          <ul class="plan-features">
            <li>✅ Full color-coded cycle calendar</li>
            <li>✅ Today's phase + basic briefing</li>
            <li>✅ What she may feel each phase</li>
            <li>✅ Do's and don'ts for each phase</li>
            <li>✅ 100% private — data stays on your device</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/app" class="btn btn-outline" style="width:100%;margin-top:24px;">Get Started Free</a>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-card pro-card">
          <div class="plan-badge pro-badge">Pro — Most Popular</div>
          <div class="plan-price">$4.99 <span class="plan-once">one-time</span></div>
          <ul class="plan-features">
            <li>✅ Everything in Free</li>
            <li>🌟 Deep daily briefings with context</li>
            <li>🌟 Intimacy guidance per phase</li>
            <li>🌟 "Insider tip" for each phase</li>
            <li>🌟 Phase transition warnings (heads-up before PMS)</li>
            <li>🌟 Partner strategy notes</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/pro" class="btn btn-primary" style="width:100%;margin-top:24px;">Unlock Pro — $4.99</a>
          <p class="plan-note">One-time payment. No subscription ever.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="final-cta">
    <div class="page-wrap" style="text-align:center;">
      <h2>Stop guessing. Start knowing.</h2>
      <p>Most relationship friction isn't about what you think it is. It's about timing. CycleWise gives you the timing.</p>
      <a href="/app" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top:32px;font-size:16px;padding:14px 32px;">Open CycleWise — Free</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    min-height: 85vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 80px 24px 60px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 0%, rgba(236,72,153,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 80% 80%, rgba(139,92,246,0.08) 0%, transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-inner { max-width: 700px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .hero-badge { margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .gradient-text {
    background: var(--gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
  .hero-sub { font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-muted); margin: 20px auto 32px; max-width: 520px; line-height: 1.7; }
  .hero-cta { display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .hero-note { margin-top: 18px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-dim); }

  /* ORBIT */
  .phase-orbit {
    margin-top: 60px;
    position: relative;
    width: 260px;
    height: 260px;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .orbit-ring {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }
  .orbit-center {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    font-size: 32px;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(236,72,153,0.4));
  }
  .orbit-phase {
    position: absolute;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    font-size: 22px;
  }
  .orbit-phase span { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .orbit-phase.menstrual { top: 0; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); }
  .orbit-phase.follicular { right: 0; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); }
  .orbit-phase.ovulation { bottom: 0; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); }
  .orbit-phase.luteal { left: 0; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); }

  /* HOW IT WORKS */
  .how-it-works { background: var(--surface); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .section-label { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--pink); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .section-sub { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 16px; margin-top: 12px; max-width: 560px; }
  .steps { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px; margin-top: 40px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .step { flex: 1; min-width: 180px; }
  .step-num {
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    background: var(--gradient);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 800; font-size: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .step h3 { margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .step p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 14px; }
  .step-arrow { font-size: 20px; color: var(--text-dim); padding-top: 8px; align-self: center; }

  /* PHASES */
  .phases-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 16px; margin-top: 40px; }
  .phase-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 24px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .phase-emoji { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .phase-label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .phase-card h3 { margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .phase-card p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .phase-tip { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); background: var(--surface2); padding: 8px 12px; border-radius: 8px; }

  .menstrual-card { border-color: rgba(248,113,113,0.2); }
  .menstrual-card:hover { border-color: rgba(248,113,113,0.4); }
  .menstrual-card .phase-label { color: #f87171; }

  .follicular-card { border-color: rgba(251,191,36,0.2); }
  .follicular-card:hover { border-color: rgba(251,191,36,0.4); }
  .follicular-card .phase-label { color: #fbbf24; }

  .ovulation-card { border-color: rgba(52,211,153,0.2); }
  .ovulation-card:hover { border-color: rgba(52,211,153,0.4); }
  .ovulation-card .phase-label { color: #34d399; }

  .luteal-card { border-color: rgba(167,139,250,0.2); }
  .luteal-card:hover { border-color: rgba(167,139,250,0.4); }
  .luteal-card .phase-label { color: #a78bfa; }

  /* PRICING */
  .pricing-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-top: 40px; }
  .pricing-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 28px;
  }
  .pro-card {
    border-color: rgba(236,72,153,0.3);
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--surface), rgba(139,92,246,0.06));
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(236,72,153,0.08);
  }
  .plan-badge {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .pro-badge { color: var(--pink); }
  .plan-price { font-size: 40px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 24px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .plan-once { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .plan-features { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .plan-features li { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .plan-note { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-top: 12px; }

  /* FINAL CTA */
  .final-cta { background: var(--surface); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .final-cta h2 { margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .final-cta p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 16px; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .hero { min-height: auto; padding: 60px 16px 40px; }
    .steps { flex-direction: column; }
    .step-arrow { display: none; }
    .phase-orbit { display: none; }
  }
</style>
